usa attractions during ptls years of rapid growth its claim 
against ptl totals 122 million 
calls to the offices of ptl attorneys were not answered the 
fairfax foreclosure request is scheduled for hearing on oct 17 
a federal judge handling ptls bankruptcy case has given the 
ministry until oct 14 to find a buyer for its properties or face 
the prospect of liquidation 
ptl filed for protection from its creditors under chapter 11 of 
bankruptcy court rules in june 1987 three months after bakker 
admitted having a sexual encounter with church secretary jessica 
hahn and resigned 
