permit to land on edwards runway 17 well pass overhead the field 
at about 40000 feet becoming subsonic you all can hear as were 
supersonic a double sonic boom when you hear that youll know 
were about five minutes from landing and then well make a 
standard approach 300 miles per hour coming down to a touchdown 
at 200 miles per hour on that lakebed 
q for mike lounge there are two men now running for president 
